<item>
            <title>[CXF-7416] Threading issue while marshalling jaxb</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-7416</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://apaste.info/ntU7&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://apaste.info/ntU7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;org.apache.cxf.interceptor.Fault: Marshalling Error: null&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.cxf.jaxb.JAXBEncoderDecoder.marshall(JAXBEncoderDecoder.java:270)&lt;br/&gt;
Caused by: java.util.ConcurrentModificationException&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.util.ArrayList$Itr.checkForComodification(ArrayList.java:901)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;:1.8.0_92&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This happened in a demo for ws-rm but probably can happen in any jaxb based service.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
